About
Central Florida Event Vendors was created in 2012 to promote a network for vendors and market managers/promoters that participate in farmers markets, arts, crafts, and other special events in Central Florida.
Currently, Central Florida Event Vendors promotes events meant to shine a light on local artisans, crafters, farmers, musicians, etc, while providing activities for the communities.
We have thousands of followers through our social media pages, including the Facebook page of
Central Florida Event Vendors
. Each major event and Saturday market also has its own Facebook page.
Please visit our event pages, including:
Winter Haven Saturday Markets
The 863 Art Fest
Haven Holiday Market
For more info contact
863ArtFest@gmail.com
or 863-258-3561.
